Command,Description
uname,Get Operating System name
uname -r,Display Linux kernel version
uname -a,Display all system information
uptime,Show how long the system has been running
uptime -p,"Show uptime in a ""pretty"" format"
uptime -s,Show the date/time the system started
lscpu,Display CPU architecture information
cat /proc/cpuinfo,Detailed CPU information
cat /proc/meminfo,Detailed RAM/Memory details
free -m,Show free and used memory in MB
free -k,Show free and used memory in KB
lsblk -a,List all block devices (disks/partitions)
fdisk -l,List partition tables
fdisk -s <partition>,Display partition size in blocks
